    },
    {
      "Text": "An update for giflib is now available for openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP1",
      "Title": "Summary",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
      "Text": "giflib is a library of gif images and provides utilities for processing images.\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\nGiflib contains a double-free vulnerability that is the result of a shallow copy in GifMakeSavedImage and incorrect error handling. The conditions needed to trigger this vulnerability are difficult but may be possible.(CVE-2026-23868)",
      "Title": "Description",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
      "Text": "An update for giflib is now available for openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP1.\n\nopenEuler Security has rated this update as having a security impact of medium. A Common Vunlnerability Scoring System(CVSS)base score,which gives a detailed severity rating, is available for each vulnerability from the CVElink(s) in the References section.",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
      "Text": "Medium",
      "Title": "Severity",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
      "Text": "giflib",
      "Title": "Affected Component",
      "Type": "General"
    }
